Package hash_tables

Class CollectionFacadeSet

java.lang.Object
hash_tables.dast.CollectionFacadeSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
SimpleSet
public class CollectionFacadeSet extends Object implements SimpleSet
Wraps an underlying Collection and serves to both simplify its API and give it a common type with the implemented SimpleHashSets.
